item.title: HacktheNorth.ph / TCon7CTF
item.description:
We won the CTF at the largest ICT and Hacker Conference in Northern Philippines!

First time participating in a live CTF competition, I had fun playing with my team. The event was also nice, cool swags and talks were informative.
